metadata.name: CBC Toys - Genesis #1
metadata.description: We are a Web3 community brand, which means that in the world of blockchain, community always comes first. With our CBC Toys - Genesis, our first pfp collection, we start our journey together as a growing community of Crypto & NFT Geeks. Each of the CBC Toys Genesis holders will get their own identity and become a member of the fam. We will move mainly in the areas of clothing/merchandise and blockchain gaming, releasing a series of P2E (Play to Earn) arcade games where players can use their NFTs to earn tokens and use them in our CBC ecosystem. Details will follow - stay tuned!
